    C->>S: send_goal(Goal)
    S-->>C: Goal Response (Accept/Reject)
    
    Note over C,S: 2. 异步执行阶段 (Topics)
    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        S->>C: publish_feedback(Feedback)
